      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything just feels so quiet lately. like i spend all day staring at these screens and i talk to people through slack or email but it doesn't feel real. i work from this apartment, i eat in this apartment, and if i didnt log on tomorrow, i dont think the silence would even change.",
