    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean by making a choice that feels real? it just feels like i'm already a ghost. if i just... stopped. like, if i didn't show up to the calls, if i didn't answer the pings, and just stayed in this silence forever. would the world even notice the difference?",
